 You can change the attributes of the user interface
 of this program to your preference and then use them
 for the current session only or save them as your
 default attributes.

 Keys:
 up & down arrows
	 change current interface attribute
 PG_UP
	 change foreground of current interface attribute
 PG_DOWN
	 change background of current interface attribute
 ESC  set attributes for current session and exit menu
 CR	 set attributes as default and exit menu
 F6	 help
